<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Privacy Policy — I Have Never</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f5f7;
      color: #1d1d1f;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    header {
      background: #3840d0;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 48px 24px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    header p  { font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.75; }
    main {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 0 24px 60px;
    }
    section { margin-bottom: 36px; }
    h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #1d1d1f;
    }
    p { font-size: 15px; color: #3d3d3f; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    ul { padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    li { font-size: 15px; color: #3d3d3f; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    a { color: #3840d0; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #999;
      padding: 24px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>I Have Never — Last updated: July 2026</p>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="card">

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>I Have Never ("the App") is a party card game developed by Herman Yurchanka. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use the App.</p>
      <p>We are committed to protecting your privacy. In short: <strong>the App does not collect, store, or share any personal data.</strong></p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
      <p>The App does not collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your name, email address, or any contact information</li>
        <li>Location data</li>
        <li>Device identifiers or advertising IDs</li>
        <li>Usage analytics or crash reports sent to us</li>
        <li>Any content you view or interact with inside the App</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>In-App Subscriptions</h2>
      <p>The App offers an optional subscription to unlock premium content. All payments and billing are processed exclusively by Apple through the App Store. We do not have access to your payment information, credit card details, or Apple ID.</p>
      <p>Apple's privacy policy governs how your payment data is handled: <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" target="_blank">apple.com/legal/privacy</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Data Stored Locally</h2>
      <p>The App stores the following data locally on your device only, using Apple's standard UserDefaults:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Whether you have completed onboarding</li>
        <li>Your language preference</li>
        <li>Whether you have an active subscription (verified through Apple)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>This data never leaves your device and is not accessible to us.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>The App does not integrate any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking SDKs. The only third-party service involved is Apple's App Store for subscription management.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Some content within the App is intended for users aged 18 and older. The App is not directed at children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect any information from children.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:geraurhapp@gmail.com">geraurhapp@gmail.com</a></p>
    </section>

  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  &copy; 2026 Herman Yurchanka. All rights reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
